MegaETH Documentation

Documentation is written in the Pandoc-flavored Markdown format. A minimal
website template (one HTML file and one CSS file) and a makefile automate the
process of converting the loose text into a website.

To build the website, make sure Pandoc and Make are installed. Then, run
"make". Files for the website will appear in public/. There is a Cloudflare
Pages automation configured for this repository on Github
(megaeth-labs/documentation) that hosts the content of public/ at
docs.megaeth.com. For that reason, always run "make" before committing and
never git-ignore any file in public/.
